# Docker build context (repo root) for the Fly worker. Keep source + manifests;
# drop installed deps, build outputs, and secrets so the image installs fresh
# (Linux yt-dlp binary) and never ships local .env.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.vercel
**/.plasmo
**/.env
**/.env.*
.git
.DS_Store
**/*.log
.playwright-mcp
docs/prototypes
